powereg

Getting started
- cargo build --release && sudo cp target/release/powereg /usr/local/bin/
- sudo powereg --install

Credits
- Heavily inspired by [auto-cpufreq](https://github.com/AdnanHodzic/auto-cpufreq), I
    just wanted a power management tool in rust bc rust is cool

